==[[Syrphinae]]== The subfamily Syrphinae is subdivided into 4 well established tribes. For table of genera, subgenera, authors and types see Mengual et al (2008)</ref>
===Tribe: [[Bacchini]]=== (=Melanostomatini) {{col-begin|width=auto}} {{col-break}} *''[[Argentinomyia]]'' <small>Lynch Arribalzaga, 1891</small> (=''Braziliana'', ''Rhysops''): NT *''[[Baccha (hoverfly)|Baccha]]'' <small>Fabricius, 1805</small>: NE OR PA *''[[Leucopodella]]'' <small>Hull, 1949</small>: NE NT *''[[Melanostoma]]'' <small>Schiner, 1860</small> (=''Plesia''): AF AU NE OR PA *''[[Platycheirus]]'' (=''Stenocheilosia''): AU NE NT OR PA **Subgenera: ***''P. ([[Carposcalis]])'' <small>Enderlein, 1938</small> ***''P. ([[Eocheilosia]])'' <small>Hull, 1949</small> ***''P. ([[Pachysphyria]])'' <small>Enderlein, 1938</small> ***''P. ([[Platycheirus]])'' <small>Lepeletier & Serville, 1828</small> ***''P. ([[Pseudoplatychirus]])'' <small>Doesburg, 1955</small> *''[[Pyrophaena]]'' <small>Schiner, 1860</small> *''[[Rohdendorfia]]'' <small>Smirnov, 1924</small>: PA *''[[Spazigaster]]'' <small>Rondani, 1843</small>: PA *''[[Syrphocheilosia]]'' <small>Stackelberg, 1864</small>: PA *''[[Talahua]]'' <small>Fluke, 1945</small>: NT *''[[Tuberculanostoma]]'' <small>Fluke, 1943</small>: NT PA *''[[Xanthandrus]]'' (=''Indosyrphus''): [[Cosmopolitan distribution|cosmopolitan]] **Subgenera: ***''X. ([[Afroxanthandrus]])'' <small>Kassebeer, 2000</small> ***''X. ([[Androsyrphus]])'' <small>Thompson, 1981</small> ***''X. ([[Xanthandrus]])'' <small>Verrall, 1901</small> {{col-break}} <gallery widths="175px" heights="175px" perrow="4"> File:Baccha bequaerti.jpg|[[Baccha (hoverfly)|Baccha]] File:Melanostoma.mellinum.-.lindsey.jpg|[[Melanostoma]] File:Platycheirus.tarsalis.-.lindsey.jpg|[[Platycheirus]] File:Platycheirus.granditarsus.-.lindsey.jpg|[[Pyrophaena]] File:Xanthandrus.comtus.-.lindsey.jpg|[[Xanthandrus]] </gallery> {{col-end}}
===Tribe: [[Paragini]]=== {{col-begin|width=auto}} {{col-break}} *''[[Paragus]]'' : AF AU NE OR PA **Subgenera: ***''P. ([[Afroparagus]])'' <small>Vujić & Radenković, 2008</small> ***''P. ([[Pandasyopthalmus]])'' <small>Stuckenberg, 1954</small> ***''P. ([[Paragus]])'' <small>Latreille, 1804</small> ***''P. ([[Serratoparagus]])'' <small>Vujić & Radenković, 2008</small> {{col-break}} <gallery widths="175px" heights="175px" perrow="4"> File:Paragus sp. August 2007-1.jpg|[[Paragus]] File:Paragus Alvesgaspar.jpg|[[Paragus|P. (Paragus)]] File:Paragus.Pandasy.jpg|[[Paragus|P. (Pandasyopthalmus)]] </gallery> {{col-end}}
===Tribe: [[Syrphini]]=== (=Chrysotoxini). In Mengual et al. (2008) this tribe was resolved into two groups.
