==Genera of uncertain affinities== This section contains a list of genera for which the bibliography does not provide a clear systematic position. These genera are not intended as ''[[incertae sedis]]'': It is likely that they have been given a formal taxonomic description or been defined in a subsequent revision, but not in the works consulted.
*''[[Pia (genus)|Pia]]'' <small>Philippi, 1865</small>: NT *''[[Poliomyia]]'' <small>Scudder, 1878</small>: NE *''[[Spheginascia]]'' <small>Meunier, 1901</small>: PA
